\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好唔健康，雖然我bmi仲低過你<br />\n不過起碼我會去增"},{"pid":"233891c9fb38414d6d494df011223eda52555397","tid":1985994,"uid":22700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T02:24:32.000Z","msg":"半個鐘先啱啱開始燒脂肪/燒肌肉<br />\n跑步唔係唔得.但個成效真係低"},{"pid":"7f61fdd46ae8895abe0162f0b7855e7b08d9614c","tid":1985994,"uid":184827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T03:56:38.000Z","msg":"我永遠都係177Cm 55Kg<br />\n<br />\n點先肥☹️"},{"pid":"20ac053a830f19e81cdabff50341df5b09db6be7","tid":1985994,"uid":34771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T04:21:28.000Z","msg":"150g protein<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9963e3569cdb1f311217bbf21c61fc4e37ba589f","tid":1985994,"uid":34771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5d2cd64eb5ff746424e947631a9768b2016aa9a6","tid":1985994,"uid":30476,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"2e5467938cda52232fae4b7ffff13c305dc6d14e","tid":1985994,"uid":489,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T15:05:56.000Z","msg":"15分鐘 5k<br />\n抖15分鐘再跑<br />\n每日兩set"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T15:37:05.000Z","msg":"香港紀錄5k 14分5x秒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T04:22:16.000Z","msg":"一生人一次"},{"pid":"13e0169c8820b4c7e61df352b2b8873951a48ea8","tid":1985994,"uid":190239,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T04:47:36.000Z","msg":"減磅同減脂肪唔同 可能你已經少左脂肪 但肌肉會令你重番 keep住一排會好d"},{"pid":"3c6ff7bedde23e5c651e4685c5d894e488f644b2","tid":1985994,"uid":1977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T04:51:49.000Z","msg":"試下扑多d野"},{"pid":"f02564895fc88d31854d65713358a967b8c36390","tid":1985994,"uid":158760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"10f4afe34e308a7d1247ceb822f62076367da4bc","tid":1985994,"uid":15636,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T22:27:16.000Z","msg":"做咁多wieght又日日食150蛋白<br />\n你股肉應該增長得唔錯<br />\n但肌肉重過脂肪<br />\n你繼續做只會增磅<br />\n一係食少啲protein <br />\n一係做少啲負重，做多啲有氧"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T06:14:38.000Z","msg":"就係因為想考消防先搏晒命練肌肉 <br />\n成身D肌肉開始爆出黎（Newbies&rsquo;s gain）<br />\n肚腩收細左好多<br />\n但就係有肚腩 點減點瘦都仲有<br />\n我之前真係冇咩點操過<br />\n<br />\n如果我冇操過肌肉依家可能唔係76KG(今朝起身去到76了）<br />\n冇操過可能得返73-74KG<br />\n<br />\n巴打講得岩其實 我減得太快<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />因爲我其實係有肌肉增長但我冇計埋落去"}]}